               resp="law-firm"><rs type="person" ref="#11988">Kraus</rs> – <rs type="institution"
                  ref="#37033">Frankf. städt.<lb xml:id="uuid_a2407760-e904-43f2-9c7c-cd65a188a481"
                  />Bühnen</rs><lb xml:id="uuid_76b3474c-5301-4678-95a1-3159fd9ffb73"/>26. JAN
               1934</note>
         </p>
